installationPath = system.tag.readBlocking("[.]../Settings/installationPathIA")[0].value
	path = installationPath +  "/Ignition/logs/wrapper.log"
	content = system.file.readFileAsString(path)
	
	if len(content) > 64000:
		result = system.tag.writeBlocking("[.]Wrapper Log" ,content[-64000:])
	
	else:
		system.tag.writeBlocking("[.]Wrapper Log",content)
